{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.1","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:1","prev_osis_id":"Jer.037.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">J\u00e9r\u00e9mie dans une citerne<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-6: cf. J\u00e9 32:1-5; 37:11, etc.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>Schephathia, fils de Matthan, Guedalia, fils de Paschhur, Jucal, fils de Sch\u00e9l\u00e9mia, et Paschhur, fils de Malkija, entendirent les paroles que J\u00e9r\u00e9mie adressait \u00e0 tout le peuple, en disant:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.37.21","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 37:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.37.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.2","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:2","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Celui qui restera dans cette ville mourra par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e, par la famine ou par la peste; mais celui qui sortira pour se rendre aux Chald\u00e9ens, aura la vie sauve, sa vie sera son butin, et il vivra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.3","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:3","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Cette ville sera livr\u00e9e \u00e0 l\u2019arm\u00e9e du roi de Babylone, qui la prendra.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.2","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.4","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:4","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Et les chefs dirent au roi: Que cet homme soit mis \u00e0 mort! Car il d\u00e9courage les hommes de guerre qui restent dans cette ville, et tout le peuple, en leur tenant de pareils discours; cet homme ne cherche pas le bien de ce peuple, il ne veut que son malheur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.3","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.5","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:5","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Le roi S\u00e9d\u00e9cias r\u00e9pondit: Voici, il est entre vos mains; car le roi ne peut rien contre vous.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.4","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.6","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:6","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Alors ils prirent J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, et le jet\u00e8rent dans la citerne de Malkija, fils du roi, laquelle se trouvait dans la cour de la prison; ils descendirent J\u00e9r\u00e9mie avec des cordes. Il n\u2019y avait point d\u2019eau dans la citerne, mais il y avait de la boue; et J\u00e9r\u00e9mie enfon\u00e7a dans la boue.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.5","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.7","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:7","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.008,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 7-13: cf. J\u00e9 39:16-18. 2 Ti 1:16-18. Mt 25:40.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>\u00c9bed-M\u00e9lec, l\u2019\u00c9thiopien, eunuque qui \u00e9tait dans la maison du roi, apprit qu\u2019on avait mis J\u00e9r\u00e9mie dans la citerne. Le roi \u00e9tait assis \u00e0 la porte de Benjamin.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.6","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.8","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:8","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>\u00c9bed-M\u00e9lec sortit de la maison du roi, et parla ainsi au roi:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.7","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.9","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:9","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>O roi, mon seigneur, ces hommes ont mal agi en traitant de la sorte J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, le proph\u00e8te, en le jetant dans la citerne; il mourra de faim l\u00e0 o\u00f9 il est, car il n\u2019y a plus de pain dans la ville.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.8","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.10","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:10","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Le roi donna cet ordre \u00e0 \u00c9bed-M\u00e9lec, l\u2019\u00c9thiopien: Prends ici trente hommes avec toi, et tu retireras de la citerne J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, le proph\u00e8te, avant qu\u2019il ne meure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.9","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.11","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:11","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>\u00c9bed-M\u00e9lec prit avec lui les hommes, et se rendit \u00e0 la maison du roi, dans un lieu au-dessous du tr\u00e9sor; il en sortit des lambeaux us\u00e9s et de vieux haillons, et les descendit \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie dans la citerne, avec des cordes.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.10","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.12","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:12","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>\u00c9bed-M\u00e9lec, l\u2019\u00c9thiopien, dit \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie: Mets ces lambeaux us\u00e9s et ces haillons sous tes aisselles, sous les cordes. Et J\u00e9r\u00e9mie fit ainsi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.11","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.13","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:13","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Ils tir\u00e8rent J\u00e9r\u00e9mie avec les cordes, et le firent monter hors de la citerne. J\u00e9r\u00e9mie resta dans la cour de la prison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.12","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:12","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.14","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:14","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.015,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Entrevue de S\u00e9d\u00e9cias et du proph\u00e8te<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 14-28: cf. J\u00e9 21:1-12; 34:1-6.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Le roi S\u00e9d\u00e9cias envoya chercher J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, le proph\u00e8te, et le fit venir aupr\u00e8s de lui dans la troisi\u00e8me entr\u00e9e de la maison de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Et le roi dit \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie: J\u2019ai une chose \u00e0 te demander; ne me cache rien.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.13","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:13","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.15","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:15","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie r\u00e9pondit \u00e0 S\u00e9d\u00e9cias: Si je te la dis, ne me feras-tu pas mourir? Et si je te donne un conseil, tu ne m\u2019\u00e9couteras pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.16","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.14","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:14","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.16","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:16","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Le roi S\u00e9d\u00e9cias jura secr\u00e8tement \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie, en disant: L\u2019\u00c9ternel est vivant, lui qui nous a donn\u00e9 la vie! Je ne te ferai pas mourir, et je ne te livrerai pas entre les mains de ces hommes qui en veulent \u00e0 ta vie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.17","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.15","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:15","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.17","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:17","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie dit alors \u00e0 S\u00e9d\u00e9cias: Ainsi parle l\u2019\u00c9ternel, le Dieu des arm\u00e9es, le Dieu d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Si tu vas te rendre aux chefs du roi de Babylone, tu auras la vie sauve, et cette ville ne sera pas br\u00fbl\u00e9e par le feu; tu vivras, toi et ta maison.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.18","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.16","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:16","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.18","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:18","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Mais si tu ne te rends pas aux chefs du roi de Babylone, cette ville sera livr\u00e9e entre les mains des Chald\u00e9ens, qui la br\u00fbleront par le feu; et toi, tu n\u2019\u00e9chapperas pas \u00e0 leurs mains.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.19","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.17","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:17","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.19","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:19","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le roi S\u00e9d\u00e9cias dit \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie: Je crains les Juifs qui ont pass\u00e9 aux Chald\u00e9ens; je crains qu\u2019on ne me livre entre leurs mains, et qu\u2019ils ne m\u2019outragent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.20","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.18","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:18","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.20","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:20","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie r\u00e9pondit: On ne te livrera pas. \u00c9coute la voix de l\u2019\u00c9ternel dans ce que je te dis; tu t\u2019en trouveras bien, et tu auras la vie sauve.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.21","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.19","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:19","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.21","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:21","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Mais si tu refuses de sortir, voici ce que l\u2019\u00c9ternel m\u2019a r\u00e9v\u00e9l\u00e9:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.22","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.20","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:20","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.22","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:22","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Toutes les femmes qui restent dans la maison du roi de Juda seront men\u00e9es aux chefs du roi de Babylone, et elles diront: Tu as \u00e9t\u00e9 tromp\u00e9, domin\u00e9, par ceux qui t\u2019annon\u00e7aient la paix; et quand tes pieds sont enfonc\u00e9s dans la boue, ils se retirent.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.23","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.21","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:21","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.23","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:23","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>Toutes tes femmes et tes enfants seront men\u00e9s aux Chald\u00e9ens; et toi, tu n\u2019\u00e9chapperas pas \u00e0 leurs mains, tu seras saisi par la main du roi de Babylone, et cette ville sera br\u00fbl\u00e9e par le feu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.24","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.22","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:22","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.24","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:24","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>S\u00e9d\u00e9cias dit \u00e0 J\u00e9r\u00e9mie: Que personne ne sache rien de ces discours, et tu ne mourras pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.25","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.23","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:23","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.25","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:25","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Si les chefs apprennent que je t\u2019ai parl\u00e9, et s\u2019ils viennent te dire: Rapporte-nous ce que tu as dit au roi, et ce que le roi t\u2019a dit, ne nous cache rien, et nous ne te ferons pas mourir,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.26","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.24","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:24","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.26","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:26","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>tu leur r\u00e9pondras: J\u2019ai suppli\u00e9 le roi de ne pas me renvoyer dans la maison de Jonathan, de peur que je n\u2019y meure.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.27","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.25","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:25","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.27","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:27","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.038.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>Tous les chefs vinrent aupr\u00e8s de J\u00e9r\u00e9mie et le questionn\u00e8rent. Il leur r\u00e9pondit enti\u00e8rement comme le roi l\u2019avait ordonn\u00e9. Ils gard\u00e8rent alors le silence et se retir\u00e8rent, car la chose ne s\u2019\u00e9tait pas r\u00e9pandue.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.28","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.26","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:26","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.28","label":"","reference":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:28","prev_osis_id":"Jer.038.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jer.039.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jer.38.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>J\u00e9r\u00e9mie resta dans la cour de la prison jusqu\u2019au jour de la prise de J\u00e9rusalem.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jer.38","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.39.1","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 39:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.39.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jer.38.27","name":"J\u00e9r\u00e9mie 38:27","id":"fra-LSG:Jer.38.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc7b36060.14738121');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc7b36060.14738121\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc7b36060.14738121","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc7b36060.14738121'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc7b36060.14738121\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}